      <title>软件公司 C3.ai 公布乐观年度预测后股价大涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/c3-ai-jumps-after-software-company-gives-upbeat-annual-forecast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受人工智能功能需求推动，软件公司 C3.ai Inc. 公布了强于预期的年度销售预测，随后其股价在尾盘交易中飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/c3-ai-jumps-after-software-company-gives-upbeat-annual-forecast</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 20:44:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠普报告称，2022 年以来 PC 销量首次增长，销售额超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/hp-reports-increased-computer-sales-with-optimism-rising-for-ai-pcs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠普公司公布的季度营收超出了分析师的预期，其中个人电脑销量两年来首次增长，这是市场期待已久的反弹的乐观信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/hp-reports-increased-computer-sales-with-optimism-rising-for-ai-pcs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 20:17:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Salesforce 公布疲软销售前景，因担心业务放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/salesforce-gives-weak-sales-outlook-with-slowdown-fears-growing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Salesforce Inc. 公布的本季度销售预期低于预期，引发人们对这家软件巨头增长放缓的担忧。盘后交易中，该公司股价下跌 14%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/salesforce-gives-weak-sales-outlook-with-slowdown-fears-growing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 20:11:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收入大幅下降，包括 Pimco 在内的 IHeart 债权人聘请顾问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/iheart-creditors-including-pimco-tap-advisers-as-revenue-slumps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[iHeartMedia Inc. 的一些债权人，包括太平洋投资管理公司 (Pacific Investment Management Co.)，已经聘请了财务和法律顾问，因为他们担心在其他负债累累的媒体公司推进债务重组之际，该公司的收入会下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/iheart-creditors-including-pimco-tap-advisers-as-revenue-slumps</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 19:49:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FBI 摧毁全球大规模僵尸电脑设备大军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/fbi-takes-down-massive-global-army-of-zombie-computer-devices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦调查局称，其已经摧毁了可能是世界上最大的僵尸网络 — — 一支由 1900 万台受感染的计算机组成的大军 — — 这些计算机被租借给黑客用于网络犯罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/fbi-takes-down-massive-global-army-of-zombie-computer-devices</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 19:22:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果暗示正在开发适用于 Android 手机的 TV+ 应用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/apple-signals-that-it-s-working-on-tv-app-for-android-phones</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司正在寻找一名高级工程师来帮助开发一款适用于 Android 的电视和体育应用程序，这表明该公司终于将其 TV+ 服务引入了竞争对手的智能手机平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/apple-signals-that-it-s-working-on-tv-app-for-android-phones</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 19:09:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
